version          0.25
categories       security
license          BSD
maintainers      nomaintainer
description      PGP packet visualizer
long_description pgpdump is a PGP packet visualizer which displays the \
                 packet format of OpenPGP (RFC 2440 + bis) and PGP \
                 version 2 (RFC 1991).
